Package: goldengateR
Type: Package
Title: In Silico Golden Gate Assembly with BsaI and BsmBI
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Stefan", "Lab", email = "you@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Simulates Golden Gate assembly of plasmids and PCR products using
    the Type IIS restriction enzymes BsaI and BsmBI. Reads GenBank or FASTA
    inputs, digests each input at all enzyme sites, attempts to ligate the
    resulting fragments into a single circular product via 4 bp sticky-end
    matching, and writes the assembled product as an annotated GenBank file.
    Returns the unique circular product if exactly one is possible; errors
    otherwise. Designed for MoClo / Yeast Toolkit / MYT workflows.
